title: AvailableActorIdentifiersPacket
description: Sends the whole list of actor identifiers at game start from the server.

Identifier List.description: CompoundTag containing a list of ActorInfo: 		rid (RuntimeId - Int), 		id (string), 		bid (BaseId - string), 		hasspawnegg (bool), 		summonable (bool)
Identifier List.x-runtime-constraint-description: Verify that the tag contains at least the "idlist" key
